The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL", "cs.AI", "cs.IR", "cs.LG", and "cs.NE". 

- "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and understanding.
- "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) is also a likely category as the paper presents an approach to build an AI-based question and answer system.
- "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper discusses the extraction of answers from a large dataset.
- "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of deep neural networks for answer extraction.
- "cs.NE" (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible category as the paper mentions the use of deep neural networks for answer extraction and generation.
